{"type": "article", "id": 22447, "title": "注重材料属性的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122226Cm7XxoweEGS1FWIn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组家具来自加拿大设计师 Thom Fougere ，除了木质家具外还包括放壁炉工具的小件和石灰岩桌子。他认为北欧、日本和加拿大在地理上有相似之处，这组家具有类似简洁实用的风格并注重保留材料本身的特征——用一块大的石灰岩当桌面，或者在木桌上使用编织元素。有一款小的边桌是几何图案的结合，圆桌面搭配三角形结构，另有一些小的圆柱装饰，在实用中带有趣味性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222237MtFUY5arEy4dOvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01495726\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122224kqu3AymPdUYBjRLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122224NZw1jhpieJDYqVtb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122225Lhap0vFV2zYDSJCe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122225IrcBKjC16yiMNzZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}